import React from "react";
import {Button,Input,Layout,Col, Row} from "antd";
import {Counter} from "./counter";

export const Counters = () =>{
    const { Header,  Content } = Layout;

    return (
    <Layout>
        <Header>
            <Row gutter={16} >
                <Col span={8}   >
                    <Input type="text" placeholder={'please enter step value'} />

                </Col>
                <Col span={2}   >
                    <Button onClick={()=>createNewCounter()} >Add Counter</Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Header>
        <Content>
            <Row gutter={16}>

                <Col span={8}>  
                    <Counter step={1} />
                </Col>

            </Row>
        </Content>
    </Layout>
    )
}
